	   <tr><td colspan=2>Definately use swords Speel. No matter what delay a weapon has your pet keeps its own natural attack rate. PLUS, give two swords of runes to your higher level air pet that has a haste bonus and massive dex. They will proc A LOT. And IMO at higher levels an air pet duel-wielding these will dish out just as much if not a little more damage than a fire pet(IN GROUPS where pets WON'T be tanking that is, I am not counting the damage shield the fire pet has).<br><br>Zuranthium/Divineshadow/Natalos/Naltec/Plantmaster/Corpusnuntia<br><br>Player of many characters on the Nameless.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
