	   <tr><td colspan=2>The proc is all that matters now, the delay doesnt affect pets anymore since a while ago they patched this issue.&nbsp;&nbsp;Necroes were soloing like crazy with low delay FS daggers.<br><br>Always use runed swords, thats what lvl 44+ necros and mages do.<br><br>That proc goes off every couple of seconds so it with a fire shield adds up.<br><br>Read Zyphyr Runnersbane's post below mine.  It sums it up plus more for lower level pets. <br><br>Also Nilerek points out the advantage of putting the mystical dagger in ranged slot.  <br>The only other better thing i know off is a sarnak ceremonial dagger (3int and some other stats) for ranged slot.<br>&nbsp;<br>Eendyar Soulseeker<br>46'th High Elf Mage <br>"Mythic Synergy"<br><a href="http://www.mythicsynergy.com" target=_new>http://www.mythicsynergy.com</a><br>Fennin Ro</td></tr>
