	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ok I will be the outsider....I use swords ALOT in groups; HOWEVER I use daggers when I am soloing.&nbsp;&nbsp;It appears (although no real testing done) that daggers cause my pet to get an extra one or two hits per round.  I solo the giants alot in Kunark and using swords I normally see 2 hits and a bash maybe a proc (56dam each hit..20dam bash...41dam proc = total damage 173...)  using daggers only with 3 hits and a bash total damage = 188 if I get one more hit damage is increased to 244. <br><br>Just my 2 coppers..but I will continue to use daggers more than swords.<br><br>Level 52 Mage<br>Khando<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
